channel.title: I may be getting rid of my Server.. -Fallen Isle-
channel.description:
Hi guys, magiklyfe here. I may be getting rid of -Fallen Isle-, I'm getting ready to dedicate all my time on Runescape. Once I either get myself a stat to 99, or get a 100+ char, I'm probably going to give away my server, if you have ever played on it, then you kno what its like.
Idk how to get pics.. if u tell me I'd be more than happy to get some on here.
Well, the reason I'm not putting this on the Download List is becuase, I want the name "Fallen Isle" to stay out there. All I'm really looking for is someone who is smart, calm, cool, and collected. Once you have the source you can do whatever, add portals, take away, move stuff.. But I'd perfer you didn't the players that come on love the server the way it is.
I used the source Godz-Pk but changed some stuff around..
Well, I'll be around.
~ N i c k
